comments.content: You are correct, this is not the place for such requests. Go to [TypeID](http://web.archive.org/web/20150418105823/http:/www.typophile.com/typeid).

This fonts is really unique and I'm not sure about this fonts. You can search this keyword "Photoshop Font List" by google or go to... [Typeid](http://web.archive.org/web/20150418105823/http:/www.typophile.com/typeid)

[Clipping Path](http://web.archive.org/web/20150418105823/http:/clippingcreationsindia.com/)

Cabriolet, Raceway, Hooptie Script, and Neon Stream are similar, but not exact matches. You can find them at [www.myfonts.com](http://web.archive.org/web/20150418105823/http:/www.myfonts.com/ "www.myfonts.com").

Font IDs only here please: [http://typophile.com/typeid](http://web.archive.org/web/20150418105823/http:/typophile.com/typeid "http://typophile.com/typeid")
